<L>__{exterior tijuana street day}
<A>__{tourist hell. a cacophony of street venders, panhandlers, and vehicular traffic. javier and manolo are speaking with a flustered young american tourist couple.}
<C>__{tourist woman}
<D>__{you're a police officer. aren't you going to take a report or something? don't you want to know what kind of car it is?}
<C>__{tourist man}
<D>__{it's a brown ford explorer }
<C>__{tourist woman}
<D>__{it was right here. it's been stolen. i want to file a report.}
